            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682290"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Career",
                "url": "/topics/career"
            },
            {
                "name": "Always",
                "url": "/topics/always"
            },
            {
                "name": "Going",
                "url": "/topics/going"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682291",
        "quote": "I've sort of decided that I can settle for being just the artist, arranger, writer and part-time engineer. That seems like enough to do.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682291"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Artist",
                "url": "/topics/artist"
            },
            {
                "name": "Settle",
                "url": "/topics/settle"
            },
            {
                "name": "Like",
                "url": "/topics/like"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682292",
        "quote": "I don't like the idea of having to reproduce a recorded song live that I sing. I have enough to do on stage. I'm really busy up there, and I'm really busy with everything I have to do for every show. Add having to worry about my voice and singing lead on a song or two, that's not something I necessarily want to do.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682292"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Voice",
                "url": "/topics/voice"
            },
            {
                "name": "Show",
                "url": "/topics/show"
            },
            {
                "name": "Idea",
                "url": "/topics/idea"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682293",
        "quote": "No one was more surprised that that first Boston record took off than the record company itself.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682293"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Boston",
                "url": "/topics/boston"
            },
            {
                "name": "Itself",
                "url": "/topics/itself"
            },
            {
                "name": "Took",
                "url": "/topics/took"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682294",
        "quote": "I will say that I know Nirvana did a show and played a few chords from 'More Than a Feeling' before they did 'Teen Spirit,' and it wasn't very good. But in all seriousness, 'Teen Spirit' was a great song. If subconsciously or somehow I had any influence on that, I'll take that as a compliment.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682294"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Before",
                "url": "/topics/before"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            },
            {
                "name": "Subconsciously",
                "url": "/topics/subconsciously"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682295",
        "quote": "Trying to get my music performed live by bar bands was a self defeating experience. It really just distracted me from what I should've been doing all along, writing and recording.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682295"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Recording",
                "url": "/topics/recording"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682296",
        "quote": "Fun is when you're writing a song and you're trying a rough shot at a demo and... it works. That's when it's fun. After that, it's work.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682296"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Song",
                "url": "/topics/song"
            },
            {
                "name": "Rough",
                "url": "/topics/rough"
            },
            {
                "name": "Works",
                "url": "/topics/works"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682273",
        "quote": "'Life, Love & Hope' is... I'm thinking 'larger picture.' I'm not trying to preach to anyone. We all get lost and caught up in our everyday problems. Your cellphone doesn't work or you got a parking ticket, you had a bad day at work. You can lose sight of the really important things in life; that's what the song is about.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682273"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Parking",
                "url": "/topics/parking"
            },
            {
                "name": "Larger",
                "url": "/topics/larger"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682284",
        "quote": "I'm very realistic in my outlook on everything in life. When I look ahead in my mind to see what's going to happen next, I see the good and I see the bad.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682284"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Mind",
                "url": "/topics/mind"
