            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682277",
        "quote": "The one thing I will say for digital, and you won't hear me say that many complimentary things about it, is that it's cheap. It pretty much enables anybody to record as long as you can deal with the sound.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682277"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Deal",
