            {
                "name": "Anybody",
                "url": "/topics/anybody"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342154",
        "quote": "We need a free media, not just freedom of speech.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342154"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Freedom",
                "url": "/topics/freedom"
            },
            {
                "name": "Speech",
                "url": "/topics/speech"
            },
            {
                "name": "Need",
                "url": "/topics/need"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342155",
        "quote": "Virtually every magazine, newspaper, TV station and cable channel is owned by a big corporation, and they've squashed stories that they don't want the public to know about.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342155"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Newspaper",
                "url": "/topics/newspaper"
            },
            {
                "name": "Big",
                "url": "/topics/big"
            },
            {
                "name": "TV",
                "url": "/topics/tv"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342156",
        "quote": "Turning corporations loose and letting the profit motive run amok is not a prescription for a more livable world.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342156"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "World",
                "url": "/topics/world"
            },
            {
                "name": "Prescription",
                "url": "/topics/prescription"
            },
            {
                "name": "Motive",
                "url": "/topics/motive"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342158",
        "quote": "The public has been sold a bill of goods about the free market being a panacea for mankind.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342158"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Market",
                "url": "/topics/market"
            },
            {
                "name": "Sold",
                "url": "/topics/sold"
            },
            {
                "name": "Panacea",
                "url": "/topics/panacea"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342169",
        "quote": "People have been convinced that growth for growth's sake is a good thing.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342169"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            },
            {
                "name": "A Good Thing",
                "url": "/topics/a_good_thing"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342171",
        "quote": "Music is an escape for me.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_342171"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Music",
