    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682257",
        "quote": "I played in a couple of really crummy bands, including one in the dorm I was in at MIT, for a year or two.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682257"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Year",
                "url": "/topics/year"
            },
            {
                "name": "Including",
                "url": "/topics/including"
            },
            {
                "name": "Couple",
                "url": "/topics/couple"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682258",
        "quote": "I don't work out a lead section and practice it for a day and then lay it down. I don't do that. The first time I do something I think is expressive or really cool, that's what's actually on the recording.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682258"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Practice",
                "url": "/topics/practice"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Recording",
                "url": "/topics/recording"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682259",
        "quote": "Musical accidents are a gold mine. The thing about accidental discoveries is they won't be made unless you put yourself in a position to make that discovery. To do that means hundreds of hours, days and weeks where you do things and don't discover anything.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682259"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            },
            {
                "name": "Weeks",
                "url": "/topics/weeks"
            },
            {
                "name": "Put",
                "url": "/topics/put"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682260",
        "quote": "I was basically a dork that hit the books and liked to build things and did all of the things that you weren't supposed to do to be popular. But somehow I ended up onstage, playing guitar in front of everybody else.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682260"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Everybody",
                "url": "/topics/everybody"
            },
            {
                "name": "Everybody Else",
                "url": "/topics/everybody_else"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682261",
        "quote": "I know everything that you can do with digital processing and digital editing inside and out, but I absolutely refuse to push the buttons and don't even want to know how to load and unload the files.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682261"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Want",
                "url": "/topics/want"
            },
            {
                "name": "Digital",
                "url": "/topics/digital"
            },
            {
                "name": "Buttons",
                "url": "/topics/buttons"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682262",
        "quote": "I detest computers. If you had a device like that 30 years ago that froze up constantly, misbehaved constantly, lost your information and screwed up when you needed it the most, it would have been laughable.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682262"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            },
            {
                "name": "Needed",
                "url": "/topics/needed"
            },
            {
                "name": "Had",
                "url": "/topics/had"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682263",
        "quote": "I'm never too ambitious when I go into the studio. I always know that I'm just going into the studio to work on or try to develop an idea that I have for a song.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682263"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Song",
                "url": "/topics/song"
            },
            {
                "name": "Always",
                "url": "/topics/always"
            },
