                "url": "/topics/bring"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682265",
        "quote": "The music that I wrote and recorded is music that I really enjoy listening to. It's just dumb luck that a lot of other people do, too.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682265"
