                "name": "Best",
                "url": "/topics/best"
            },
            {
                "name": "I Think",
                "url": "/topics/i_think"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682274",
        "quote": "I'm certainly aware of the fans. I'm always hoping that what I'm doing is something they'll like, because I do appreciate them. But, no, when I get into the studio, it's all about what I like. It's the same thing that led me to the possibility of making that first Boston album, which was to divorce myself from all other influences.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682274"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
