                "name": "Studio",
                "url": "/topics/studio"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682275",
        "quote": "I take chances. I don't limit myself. I don't think anybody who listens to Boston would have predicted hearing a female rapper on the beginning of the song 'Sail Away.' But that's what fit.",
