    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682279",
        "quote": "The lyrics are always the last thing I do. I always have a recording of basic tracks and maybe some of the lead work. I'll sit back and listen to it, and I'll just concentrate on what kind of feeling it gives me. My goal writing the lyrics is to not disrupt that feeling.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682279"
