    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682280",
        "quote": "I took classical piano for a couple of years, but I sort of lost interest - I couldn't read a note today if I tried. I still enjoy that stuff, and I think I naturally gravitate towards the classical licks; in fact, I know that I do. I gravitate towards the classical licks that I heard by famous old composers.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682280"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Composers",
