                "url": "/topics/note"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682281",
        "quote": "The pressure is all self-imposed, and it's to live up to the expectations of people who are going to shell out their hard-earned cash to listen to the music. It's actually more than that, though. I wouldn't want to make a record that didn't live up to my expectations.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682281"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Music",
                "url": "/topics/music"
            },
            {
                "name": "Listen",
                "url": "/topics/listen"
            },
            {
                "name": "Out",
                "url": "/topics/out"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682282",
        "quote": "I can sit down at a piano or with a guitar and just chug away for hours and be perfectly content with whatever comes out. But when it comes to something that somebody else is going to listen to, then I do feel a great deal of pressure to do something that's exceptional, at least in what I consider to be at the limits of what I can do.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Tom Scholz",
            "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682282"
        },
