    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/tom_scholz_682286",
        "quote": "I'm one of those artists that doesn't actually hate my old hits. I love Boston music. I really like 'More than a Feeling.' After playing it to myself in a basement for such a long time, I'm happy to do it out on stage.",
